snippet.description:
All music recorded and written by John Kiernan.

Are you looking for a custom wrestling entrance theme or walk out music? 
Contact via email at johnkiernanmusic@gmail.com.

Amber Rodriguez Theme - Perfect Like Me (Official Music Video)

• Instagram: www.instagram.com/johnkiernanmusic
• Twiter: www.twitter.com/jkiernanguitar
• Website: www.johnkiernanmusic.com

About John Kiernan:
John Kiernan is a wrestling entrance theme song composer from New Jersey. John is the in-house composer for the United Wrestling Network and has written original entrance themes for various talents from Ring of Honor, New Japan Pro Wrestling, Major League Wrestling, All Elite Wrestling, and many more. John has also performed domestically and internationally in Shanghai, China at MusikMesse with his original music and his previous work with Etherius. John has performed with and provided support for a myriad of artists including Slash from Guns N’ Roses, Myles
Kennedy and The Conspirators, Gus G (former guitarist for Ozzy Ozbourne), Andy James, Foxy Shazzam!, and many more.

To learn more about John Kiernan, visit www.johnkiernanmusic.com

snippet.title: [STATION] AMBER 엠버 'Borders' MV
snippet.description:
SM STATION’s 7th Track “Borders” sung by Amber has been released.
Listen and download on iTunes & Apple Music, Spotify, and Google Play Music http://smarturl.it/Borders_STATION

Also here is a message from AMBER :

Before the song is released there are a couple things I'd like to share. This song took me a lot of courage to write because I was always apprehensive of the subject it talked about. I've been doing this job for a long time and right now I speak not as Amber of f(x) nor "celebrity" Amber, but just Amber. Just plain, simple, human Amber. "Borders" is more than a song; no glamorous concepts, no "trying to be cool." Its a raw and real story about reality. Its shares, not only about my personal experiences but of people very close to me. Everyone involved in this project- the producers, my team DPR, the actors, to the staff- were people specifically chosen as they have never given up on me and believed in my vision. For that, I want to thank them for making this possible for me. When you guys listen to "Borders", there is just one thing i wish everyone could take from it: NEVER give up on yourself. There is always hope in the midst of this dark, demanding world. In the end, live for those that did not get the chance to and just keep fighting. Always, thank you you guys. You guys made it possible. 

노래 나오기전에 여러분한테 몇까지 말하고 싶습니다. 이 노래를 쓸때 많은 용기를 냈어요 왜냐하면 이 주제가 사람들한테 말하고 오픈 하는 자체가 많은 겁을 갖고 있었어요. 제가 연예 활동 한지 오래됐지만 지금 저는 에프엑스의 엠버, 연예인 엠버로서 말하고 있지않습니다. 지금 그냥 엠버. 인간 엠버입니다. 보더스"는 그냥 노래가 아닙니다. 콘셉 짜서 멋있게 만들으려고 하는것도 없어요. 그냥 진심, 솔직함 담은 현실 이야기입니다. 제 이야기과 제 친한테 사름들의 이야기. 이 프로젝트 만들면서 작곡 같이 하는 친구들부터, 제 제작팀 DPR, 연기자들, 스탭분들까지 제가 직접 골랐습니다. 그 이유는 제 옆에 있으면서 포기 절대 하지 않았고 제가 갖고 있는 환상을 믿어주는 분들이기때문에. 그친구들한테 감사하다는 말을 다시 하고 싶습니다. "보더스" 듣고 이 매세지 전하고 싶어요: 절대 자기 자신한테 포기하지말아요. 이 어두운 힘든 세상에도 희망 항상 있습니다. 마지막으로 살 기회 없었던 사람들위해서 살아요. 힘을 내세요. 여러분 항상 감사 드려요. 제가 이렇게까지 할 수 있는 이유는 여러분입니다.

http://www.youtube.com/Amberliumusic
http://www.facebook.com/fx.smtown

http://www.instagram.com/smtownstation
http://www.facebook.com/station.smtown

snippet.title: Amber Divari  -  Blue Ocean (Summer chill out music)
snippet.description:
Das neue Album "Pandora" nimmt uns mit auf eine Reise durch die Kontinente unserer Erde.

Amber Divari schlägt eine Brücke zwischen independent Pop Einflüssen der 80er gemischt mit Elementen von House und Techno/Trance.
 you are welcome to donate
Hier kannst Du etwas spenden um die Musikerin zu unterstützen …. Thanks so much

https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=MF7B3W45VLEBG&source=url

Bei der sehr eindrucksvollen Variablen musikalischenGestaltung der Musik - Stücke gibt Amber Divari eine vollkommen neue Art Ihres Musikstils an. Ein sehr vielfältiges Spektrum an musikalischen Einflüssen, welches keine Elemente ausspart. Zu hören sind elektronische Einflüsse aus House und Trance/Techno, klassische Instrumente wie Chello oder Harfe. Naturgeräusche und feine Einlagen einer solistischen E-Gitarre.

Amber Divari bridges the gap between independent pop influences from the 80s mixed with elements of house and techno / trance.
 
With the very impressive variable musical design of the music pieces, Amber Divari indicates a completely new way of her music style. A very wide spectrum of musical influences, which spares no elements. Electronic influences from house and trance / techno, classical instruments such as chello or harp can be heard. Nature sounds and fine inlays of a solo electric guitar.
 
The album "Pandora" takes us on a journey through the continents of our earth.

Thanks for your likes and shares 

www.amberdivari.com

snippet.title: Davisson Brothers Band & Amber Lawrence - Greatest Show On Earth (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Written by the Davisson Brothers, Amber Lawrence, and Rob Synder, and produced by Dan Frizsell, “Greatest Show On Earth” was a labor of love with both parties at each end of the world doing their part to get the quality sound to make it a world-class production.  They ended up with over one hundred tracks and eight different acoustic guitar parts with guest musicians, Bryan Sutton, who wrote and played additional guitar, banjo, and mandolin parts. Everyone involved did their part to assist in making the duet as big and powerful as could be to ensure the poignant lyrical message could be heard loud and clear.

“We recommend everyone listening to this at high volume and a lot of bass!  We wish nothing but good to everyone and we hope this brightens someone’s day when they hear it. That’s all this song was meant to do--bring positivity to the world," says Chris Davisson.

A special thank you to the fans that submitted their own videos!

Listen to Greatest Show on Earth now: https://orcd.co/greatestshowonearth
